title: Edgar Allan Poe - Comics Collection
description:
Edgar Allan Poe - Comics Collection
(December, 2013.)

All files in CBR and/or CBZ format
Download CDisplay here - http://www.cdisplay.me/

This is collection of comics based on or inspired by work of Edgar Allan Poe.

List:
- Edgar Allan Poe - The Fall of the House of Usher and Other Tales o f Terror TPB (Del Rey, 2005)
- Edgar Allan Poe's - The Conqueror Worm (Dark Horse, 2012)
- Edgar Allan Poe's - The Fall of the House of Usher 1 of 2 (Dark Horse, 2013)
- Edgar Allan Poe's - The Fall of the House of Usher 2 of 2 (Dark Horse, 2013)
- Edgar Allan Poe's - The Raven and the Red Death (Dark Horse, 2013)
- Haunt of Horror - Edgar Allan Poe 1 of 3 (Max, 2006)
- Haunt of Horror - Edgar Allan Poe 2 of 3 (Max, 2006)
- Haunt of Horror - Edgar Allan Poe 3 of 3 (Max, 2006)
